what goes up is an american comedy-drama film distributed by sony pictures entertainment starring hilary duff , steve coogan , josh peck , olivia thirlby , and molly shannon , directed by jonathan glatzer and co-written by glatzer and robert lawson . coogan also serves as an executive producer . it premiered on may 8 , 2009 at the 3rd annual buffalo niagara film festival . what goes up was released in the us through sony pictures and three kings productions in select theaters on may 29 , 2009 and expanded to more theaters the following week . cities included los angeles , new york , las vegas , buffalo , boston and chicago . the movie grossed $ &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in its opening weekend .